Name: Meilou
Alliance: Chongsheng sanshê (Chongsheng three shê ritual alliance)
Village_Settlement: The total population is approximately 1000 people.
Surname_Groups: The main surname group is the Chen 陈.
Village_Temples: 1) Chongshenggong 崇圣宫: The main gods are Wugu shenxian 五谷神仙, Qitian dasheng 齐天大圣. Secondary gods include Puji shenghou 普济圣候, Dujiao jiangjun 独角将军, and Tiangong yuanshuai 田公元帅.
